                <note rend="inline" type="source">437.11H23/94: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Cuba</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Reed</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-10-01T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 1, 1929—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 6:45 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>105. My telegram No. 102, September 28, noon.<note n="38" xml:id="d946fn38">Not
                        printed.</note> Harrah arbitration. Protocol signed this afternoon. Shall
                    forward it by pouch leaving tomorrow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Reed</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
